===Verb===
{{en-verb|rais|ing}}

# To cause to [[rise]].
#:'''''Raise''' your hand if want to say something''.
# To collect.
#:''He '''raises''' a lot of money for charity.''
# To be brought up; to [[mature]]
#:''Chew with your mouth shut - were you '''raised''' in a barn?''

